        "subject": "LU-7754 osd: osd-zfs should not wait indefinitely for a TXG",
        "message": "LU-7754 osd: osd-zfs should not wait indefinitely for a TXG\n\nif the transaction is too big for a reason, then dmu_tx_assign(TXG_WAIT)\nwill be waiting indefinitely. instead try to fit a TXG few times and\ngive up with -ENOSPC.\n\nChange-Id: I55c12a14e18a9efc2c1cb34c915c14b029102001\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
